.TH SM-LS 1  "ls " 
.SH NAME
ls \- List entities
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBls\fR [\fB\-\-findings\fR] [\fB\-\-requirements\fR] [\fB\-\-notes\fR] [\fB\-\-scope\fR] [\fB\-\-severity\fR] [\fB\-\-status\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIPATH\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
List entities
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-findings\fR
